&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for an enthusiastic and motivated individual to join the award winning Estates Department team at Dorset County Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a new and challenging post, initially for a one year fixed contract period, to further improve our delivery against operational and strategic goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a working supervisor position and applicants will need to be able to demonstrate a sound knowledge of the maintenance and construction industry and have experience of supervising a team in a demanding and varied working environment.&lt;/p&gt;
